CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Men, including Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence shaking man's hand, and women, including Jessie Vann shaking hands with another woman wearing African dress, gathered in Office of the Mayor, City County Building
